/* =========================================================================
   data.js — Course catalogue: metadata now, vocabulary on demand.

   Only the index below is parsed at start-up (a few tens of kB). The words
   themselves live in js/data/<courseId>.js and are pulled in by loadCourse()
   the first time that course is opened, then merged into these very objects —
   so anything holding a reference to a lesson sees its items appear in place.

   `n` is the item count, kept here so cards, progress and the SRS can do their
   arithmetic without downloading a single word.

   Adding a language: add an entry here AND a matching js/data/<id>.js.
   ========================================================================= */

